{"tid":27014,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"admin請講下del post標準","createTime":"2016-12-07T05:21:09.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T07:06:21.000Z","uid":28264,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"88e60ea5d4ce3d1d793fbea8177529d83c323dda","tid":27014,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:21:09.000Z","msg":"lihkg係高登既延伸<br />\n大家都拎左高登既一套放入lihkg<br />\n簡單d講就係 「超自由既」既討論風氣<br />\n例如ptgf,自殺 等既爭議post係高登都唔會話被del<br />\n而「超自由既」就係高登一直點解咁紅既原因<br />\n<br />\n對於呢d post點處理 我就沒乜意見 只希望admin公開個規距<br />\n<br />\n如果lihkg唔係行呢一套 請公開咁講明呢個論壇既規距係咩<br />\n當年膠登都有定一套規距出黎<br />\n亦希望admin就每一個del既post得出解釋 只需要好簡單咁佢犯左咩事就ok 比大家知道個罪名 唔洗深入講解 因為大家會有公論<br />\n<br />\n而且希望admin唔好太過人治 班會員講咩就做咩 跟規距做就好了<br />\n特別對於爭議post 唔係只會變成膠登2.0<br />\n<br />\n希望admin可以睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea5af3ea0ddd6715dda40bdeb52da21427c42e78","tid":27014,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:22:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df465d6ee9249a9698778bddd8e8e3c68c968527","tid":27014,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:23:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a3cde7cd14393495cdd955b2ba70bf7b897c878","tid":27014,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:23:56.000Z","msg":"當年膠登就係太過重視班傻閪講咩<br />\n佢地講咩就做咩 最後就收撚左皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0822ca81838588bac3a634b18b0b1a2c138c2268","tid":27014,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:24:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91dd61df92fceff473ca37bc68cb4a9dbc3df3ea","tid":27014,"uid":28264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:25:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor